metadata.name: Black Tiger
metadata.description:
New year Black Tiger Shojo

I drew this to celebrate 2022
I thought about how to draw a cute tiger girl and completed this picture
I hope you stay healthy in 2022 when you see this picture

I will continue to grow as an artist. You can look forward to it

To briefly explain the character
She likes to drink and play ball
I sometimes play with my tail, but it's very cute

Pixel 2150 x 3035   DPI 300

Creative by SOLar
